description: The demolition of the existing buildings on the site of 72-78 Conington Road SE13 and the construction of a seven to ten storey building, incorporating balconies, comprising 3 commercial units on part of the ground floor, 187 one bedroom, 56 two bedroom and 27 studio self-contained flats, together with associated landscaping and provision of bin stores, bicycle stores, 9 motorcycle parking spaces and 50 car parking spaces at basement level with access onto Conington Road.
